**About**

Professional with 15 years of experience in digital product, strategic content, B2B marketing and events. I lead projects that integrate these areas into coordinated operations for brands, communities and institutional projects.

My work covers roadmap, editorial operations, communications, B2B marketing, stakeholder relations and performance tracking. I coordinate cross-functional teams, vendors, media partners and senior leadership, with a focus on aligning strategy, governance and execution.

I have worked across digital campaigns, SEO, SEM, performance analysis, editorial planning, audiovisual production, proprietary events, automation and AI tools applied to marketing and content operations.

Available for conversations about opportunities, partnerships and projects.

